annotated-doc (0.0.4-0ubuntu1~ppa1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging of annotated-doc 0.0.4 for the Avalan PPA.
  * Transitive runtime dep of python3-fastapi. Not in Debian; zero
    runtime deps so the Depends is just ${python3:Depends}.
  * Ship a quilt patch (pyproject-license-for-noble) rewriting the
    PEP 639 `license = "MIT"` + `license-files = [...]` pair to the
    legacy `license = { file = "LICENSE" }` table form -- the
    Noble-setuptools workaround the rest of the per-dep tree uses.
    Build backend is pdm-backend (Noble ships python3-pdm-backend).

 -- Avalan Packaging Team <avalan@avalan.ai>  Tue, 19 May 2026 00:40:00 -0300
